data.description: Step into this charming home right out of story book and nestled in center of La Marque in quiet subdivision on a large corner lot at 2505 N Houston, La Marque. This 3-bed, 2-bath home sits on a spacious corner lot with a double-wide driveway. The property boasts original hardwood floors, a marble-tiled primary shower, and elegant crystal doorknobs. It's move-in ready with all the appliances and more - two refrigerators, microwave, washer and dryer all included. With recent windows and gas lines, exterior paint in 2019 and interior paint in 2018, plus A/C replaced in 2017, it's both timeless and updated. Best of all, there's no HOA, and it's never flooded, according to the seller. Enjoy easy access to the freeway and nearby shopping. Make this your home sweet home!
